  "summary": "This ERC standardizes an interface for contract-layer consensus-agnostic verifiable cross-chain bridging, through which we can define a new global token inherited from [ERC-20](./eip-20.md)/[ERC-721](./eip-721.md) over multi-chains. ### Figure.1 Architecture ![img](../assets/eip-6358/img/o-dlt.png) With this ERC, we can create a global token protocol, that leverages smart contracts or similar mechanisms on existing blockchains to record the token states synchronously. The synchronization could be made by trustless off-chain synchronizers.",
  "title": "Cross-Chain Token States Synchronization"
